      description: "Specifies the protocol-independent default value for the same settings in [IPv6AcceptRA], [DHCPv4], and [DHCPv6] sections below. Takes a boolean, or the special value route. See also the same setting in [DHCPv4] below. Defaults to unset.Added in version 256.",
