      description: "Configures IPv6 Hop Limit. Takes an integer in the range 1…255. For each router that forwards the packet, the hop limit is decremented by 1. When the hop limit field reaches zero, the packet is discarded. When unset, the kernel's default will be used.Added in version 228.",
