      description: "Configures IPv6 Retransmission Time. The time between retransmitted Neighbor Solicitation messages. Used by address resolution and the Neighbor Unreachability Detection algorithm. A value of zero is ignored and the kernel's current value will be used. Defaults to unset, and the kernel's current value will be used.Added in version 256.",
